                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <button id="start-review-process" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-amber-700 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-lg pulse-soft">
                        üì∏ Prova Subito - √à Gratis!
                    </button>
                    <a href="/register" class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:text-amber-700 transition-all">
                        Crea Account
